      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "DEFINICIÓN",
        "guid": "VfCUXxbcpBBDKC_pCjXw0w",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Enfermedad ocular autoinmune + inflamación tejidos orbitarios",
            "guid": "P-gMvUlxzn0rlh_yH_yZjA",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "EPIDEMIOLOGÍA",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "4",
            "parent": "3",
            "text": "50% pacientes con Graves → diagnóstico clínico",
            "guid": "VmfNOFciNGkqhd6YTPQOVQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "5",
            "parent": "3",
            "text": "Relación con\nestado tiroideo:",
            "guid": "WzX14lFhc7wznF-nRiPhyQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "6",
                "parent": "5",
                "text": "90% → hipertiroidismo",
                "guid": "a3tNFCQQv50D5HIzXfgXTw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "7",
                "parent": "5",
                "text": "10% → otras etapas (eutiroidismo/hipotiroidismo postratamiento)",
                "guid": "XOzNwRtjOt8TL4DmAbdY4w",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "8",
            "parent": "3",
            "text": "Gravedad:",
            "guid": "IBorrg4FvM1GKL8nAlFJQg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "9",
                "parent": "8",
                "text": "20-30% → clínicamente relevante",
                "guid": "f0OBn0UIBds9WB1mVTQV_g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "10",
                "parent": "8",
                "text": "5% → grave (neuropatía óptica distiroidea)",
                "guid": "W-Sp6wCATU9fagbSG8y2qA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "11",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "FISIOPATOLOGÍA",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "12",
            "parent": "11",
            "text": "Inicio → Linfocitos vs antígenos comunes tiroides/órbitas",
            "guid": "SfIbzQsAJsQ7yVA1IFnpBQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "13",
            "parent": "11",
            "text": "Proceso: ↑ Vol. músculos extraoculares + tejido conjuntivo/adiposo retroorbitario\n→ • Inflamación • ↑ GAG (glucosaminoglicanos) hidrofílicos + ác. hialurónico",
            "guid": "YiJbLmZPLs1tTfdaPVhREA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "14",
            "parent": "11",
            "text": "Mecanismo: Células T → ↑citoquinas (TNF-α + interferón-γ) → Fibroblastos → ↑GAG\n→ ↑Presión osmótica → ↑líquido → ↑Presión intraorbitaria →",
            "guid": "N7CiiSDqVwEDfDLZIyvvnQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "15",
                "parent": "14",
                "text": "↓Drenaje venoso",
                "guid": "RPsWngdgpQwBJAbtIefkXw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "16",
                "parent": "14",
                "text": "↓Movilidad músculos extraoculares",
                "guid": "IsPf6xRTh9Mjnz1CQt4LmQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "17",
                "parent": "14",
                "text": "Desplazamiento anterior órbitas",
                "guid": "IllEoWnH_GpFL1TbIZzGQA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "18",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "CAUSA\nPROBABLE",
        "guid": "LtACRQKHckF20Nw_CrSsMA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "19",
            "parent": "18",
            "text": "Activación inmune × TRab en adipocitos/fibroblastos orbitarios",
            "guid": "Awe_kVY64xEmgWLYTPnbXg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "20",
            "parent": "18",
            "text": "Otros autoantígenos posibles: anti-IGF-1 + tiroglobulina",
            "guid": "YTsJ1WJKsw1tU8RjQ11lAw",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "21",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "DIAGNÓSTICO\nDIFERENCIAL",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "22",
            "parent": "21",
            "text": "Esp. forma unilateral\n→ considerar:",
            "guid": "SJnh2lqhu70AtbYTAEqEZA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "23",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Pseudotumor orbitario",
                "guid": "e4wSvgQx6OwjdnQBQIcpXA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "24",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Miositis orbitaria",
                "guid": "C5KN-CSaeu5ibw28LlZt4w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "25",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Fístula seno cavernoso",
                "guid": "OO4CwgYOSv5xNHl8W0dHYw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "26",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Celulitis orbitaria",
                "guid": "b9ZHaDZjzld85A2jHqZJrQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "27",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Tumores orbitarios",
                "guid": "OOtAmXO06eIpWvXdO_MAKg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "28",
                "parent": "22",
                "text": "Miopía grave",
                "guid": "Se_M80_cWLYI7NuIKyrWyQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "29",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "EVALUACIÓN\nCLÍNICA",
        "guid": "UOJbqG898eB7C3ICTG5uZg",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "30",
            "parent": "29",
            "text": "2 parámetros complementarios: \n→ Evaluar simultáneamente ambos parámetros",
            "guid": "MicLw3ZAn-tuiDvMesDtng",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "31",
                "parent": "30",
                "text": "Actividad (inflamación)\n→ Escala CAS",
                "guid": "c2_azB6B5gMM9ZfCfwJoxQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "32",
                    "parent": "31",
                    "text": "• Score ≥3 → activa",
                    "guid": "Qxxg8m9kpX4tWNaofApjtA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "33",
                    "parent": "31",
                    "text": "• Score <3 → inactiva",
                    "guid": "dXLwfR6NUCVXUasXZUk35Q",
                    "children": []
