                "id": "69",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Graves",
                "guid": "CR7USDuMf319_WsparfoVg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "70",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Tiroiditis Hashimoto",
                "guid": "GmPhuj8jB801duxnDS6JfA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "71",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Otras enf. autoinmunes",
                "guid": "dkaeJxPEAE9R4tmxTC84VA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "72",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "Sexo: • + frecuente mujeres • Hombres → evolución + grave",
            "guid": "CIQ55GuL19UEto_tOBZ_qQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "73",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "Tabaco (4,5): • Riesgo 7.7× > en fumadores\n• Mecanismo:",
            "guid": "fTniKEx_viYM8yPfF53D4g",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "74",
                "parent": "73",
                "text": "↑volumen tejido conectivo orbital",
                "guid": "C6LF9EJqEEYkzE1eAelkGw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "75",
                "parent": "73",
                "text": "↑GAG + adipogénesis →\nexposición-dependiente",
                "guid": "Vi4QlnavJw9OGJxvXrJKeg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "76",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "• Recomendación: cese inmediato en\ntodo paciente Graves (esp. con ODT)",
                    "guid": "Yjr-5FLPLFwWyMojMBGs9w",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "77",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "Disfunción\ntiroidea:",
            "guid": "e6cD5Bj7iVEn78xHJ3D6KQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "78",
                "parent": "77",
                "text": "• Hipertiroidismo persistente → + riesgo ODT grave",
                "guid": "ATMbHypVokJWDKOHAaCUUQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "79",
                "parent": "77",
                "text": "• Hipotiroidismo → deletéreo × ↑TSH",
                "guid": "V22951z4qilaT1WmcIolKA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "80",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "Tratamiento\nhipertiroidismo:",
            "guid": "HqYM1CjRqKQSxWCxG9_u_A",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "81",
                "parent": "80",
                "text": "• I131 → + riesgo vs tionamidas/cirugía",
                "guid": "dVFmyh-4hJEzfbLeAPQsvg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "82",
                "parent": "80",
                "text": "• Post-I131: 15% casos → ODT nueva/progresión (2-6 meses)",
                "guid": "YiKU11hKADwC3ZDZOFClbQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "83",
                "parent": "80",
                "text": "• Prevención: glucocorticoides + I131",
                "guid": "TvknS1D2LUkXAu_nMTQmMA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "84",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "TRab:",
            "guid": "I8VZpS3LugphRdMnH2xdiQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "85",
                "parent": "84",
                "text": "• Títulos elevados → + frecuencia/gravedad ODT",
                "guid": "RsdDWwk1n29G3VeyR_peeg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "86",
            "parent": "67",
            "text": "Otros:",
